an class=\"red\">當連登係FB玩嘅死狗公</span></strong></strong>唔少<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OoZJ1iP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOoZJ1iP.jpg&h=ab6c268d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qQcSUDQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqQcSUDQ.png&h=7000e983&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 恥笑毒撚 佢主人濟癲 老死浮雲 多次恥笑毒撚 話毒撚社會垃圾 反社會人渣 同依班人為伍嘅會員#370062都唔好得去邊 明明自己都係毒撚 正一25仔<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FYD3gS1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFYD3gS1.png&h=ac29add3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/brgsJxB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbrgsJxB.png&h=0d69bccc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UDk9crV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUDk9crV.png&h=8b94f1f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WhCWRgK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWhCWRgK.png&h=d9791dac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"37030ffb0de780857bb97eb9f5f923f5c7bfe738","tid":2342671,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T09:55:38.000Z","msg":"真係好乖乖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96baa83171193b1e1a0b52d871e09894e4917be7","tid":2342671,"uid":200529,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T09:56:27.000Z","msg":"哎啊哎啊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FNJbFe6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFNJbFe6.png&h=c22d0404&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e403c2c4a03fa64e69588bf5d5929d33ccb5f8d","tid":2342671,"uid":305269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T09:56:44.000Z","msg":"關愛座全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as